Cellular and Molecular Aspects of Managing Familial Hypercholesterolemia: Recent 
and Emerging Therapeutic Approaches.

Taheri F(1), Taghizadeh E(2)(3), Baniamerian F(3), Rostami D(4), Rozeian A(3), 
Mohammad Gheibi Hayat S(5), Jamialahmadi T(6), Reiner Ž(7), Sahebkar 
